{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And sometimes I think about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "What expression of love.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When I see some-- a kitten-- a kitten doing this, I think-- I think about what my mom did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I can't say enough about both of my parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I just wished I had the gift of having them around longer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But the environment at home was excellent, warm, loving, caring.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They gave me a childhood like no child could ask for anything better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Material things, they did the best they could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But in terms of attention and love, it was much more than one could ask for.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother and I were, perhaps, opposite in terms of interest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our characters were the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, we grew up in the same environment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His interest-- he was a more serious type.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If he would grow in this country, he probably would've been in advanced classes and learning in school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was always ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The difference in our age was, like, 20 months-- actually, let's see, 18 months difference in ages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was 18 months older, and yet he was much more serious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was the typical kid with the soccer and, kind of, activities in school, and mischievous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he was a more serious type-- books that I've heard of-- he was in fourth and fifth grade, he was reading Tolstoy and Victor Hugo, and poetry by Polish Adam Mickiewicz, Henryk Sienkiewicz-- stuff that I wouldn't read until I got into eighth-- eighth grade.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was way ahead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Scholarly, much, much advanced for his age.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At home, sometimes I would resent, because the other kids had brothers they would play soccer with, you know, or play a game of chess, checkers-- not chess, checkers.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
